keyMappings:
# Insert your preferred key mappings here.
map K scrollPageUp
map J scrollPageDown
map g^ firstTab
map <C-j> scrollFullPageDown
map <C-k> scrollFullPageUp
map yl LinkHints.activateModeToCopyLinkUrl
# Open multiple links in new tabs
map gl LinkHints.activateModeWithQueue
unmap >>
unmap <<
map < moveTabLeft
map > moveTabRight
unmap d
map dd removeTab
map <C-r> restoreTab
map u goBack
map U goForward
" Open a Link in current tab using a new tab
map F LinkHints.activateModeToOpenInNewForegroundTab
map H previousTab
map L nextTab
searchEngines:
b: https://www.baidu.com/s?wd=%s Baidu
git: https://github.com/search?q=%s GitHub
g: https://www.google.com/search?q=%s Google
y: https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=%s Youtube
w: https://www.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Special:Search&search=%s Wikipedia
l: https://www.google.com/search?q=%s&btnI I'm feeling lucky...
